    <content>&lt;P&gt;Great questions.&amp;nbsp; Sometimes I will read parts of a book and skip chapters - for example, any book about the Kennedys - I'll skip chapters.&amp;nbsp; I don't think I simply stopped reading a book.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I do read multiple books at the same time - I am usually reading a fiction, biography and self help books all at the same time!&lt;/P&gt;</content>
