      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/82</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I would think you would have one production instance with Meter to Cash and Finance in the same instance.&amp;nbsp; The "cash" part is likely the biggest source of Accounts Receivable and one instance makes auditing finance easier.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
